  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can expend 1 point of mental focus to draw out the corruption from a creature. You must touch the target with your implement to use this power. This ability functions as either @Compendium[pf1.spells.6l904edkt8jv9jor]{Neutralize Poison} or @Compendium[pf1.spells.ocbjt6z7amc3yn8w]{Remove Disease}, using your occultist level as the caster level.</p>\n<p>Each use of this ability can cure only one poison or one disease.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 5th level to select this focus power.</p>"
    },
